   <head>Epigrammi - XLVIII. De Cyparisso Puero.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Flebat adhuc moerens cervo Cyparissus ademto,</l>
     <l n="2">Quum sua conspexit cortice membra tegi.</l>
     <l n="3">Delius exclamat: Quid nostro, silva, dolore</l>
     <l n="4">Crescis? Tu Daphnen, tu Cyparisson habes.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
